0Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>AMD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明顯有heart<br />\nIntel當班顧客狗咁撚</blockquote><br />\n數唔係咁計，呢單野明顯係amd未整好就丟出街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n Intel呢咁？<br />\nIntel條條ram上到？<br />\nIntel幾時會再更新？<br />\nIntel咪出啲矽脂撚人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nintel上唔到咩？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797213276b9540b88033dda1ab4496a4dcebdbb9","tid":232440,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> Intel呢咁？<br />\nIntel條條ram上到？<br />\nIntel幾時會再更新？<br />\nIntel咪出啲矽脂撚人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIntel近幾代的確.問題唔太大<br />\n<br />\n因為好老實講.個架構都冇乜改到.最多都係換下製程.加下少少新技術又新一代<br />\n<br />\n所以都冇咩特別野<br />\n<br />\n不過Intel個Cooler真係好廢.一代差過一代.外表雖然唔明顯睇得出.不過其實係愈黎愈細隻.散熱片.愈黎愈簿.高度愈黎愈矮.<br />\n<br />\n同埋的確cut cost得愈黎愈多.skylake都俾人話pcb又簿左<br />\n<br />\n乜都縮哂水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9fd10a9788dadf9eb340fc3e91eea0695f8a420","tid":232440,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>AMD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明顯有heart<br />\nIntel當班顧客狗咁撚</blockquote><br />\n數唔係咁計，呢單野明顯係amd未整好就丟出街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n事實上都係<br />\n<br />\n不過都公道d講.好多新產品.推出個時都有唔少問題<br />\n<br />\n不過Ryzen的確係比較多<br />\n<br />\n其實都唔知amd想點.d人都等左咁耐.都唔差在再等多一兩三個月<br />\n<br />\n如果AMD一開始Delay多一兩個月.成件事會好好多<br />\n<br />\n當然.而家其實都唔係差<br />\n<br />\n而且AMD都改得算快.都睇得出佢既誠意既</blockquote><br />\n我完全唔介意呢單野，Ryzen 一出就已經買左用緊<br />\n但冇理由將呢d&quot;問題&quot;當成amd 有heart黎計架嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試試intel整單一樣既野會唔會畀人屌到飛起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c97358f7c6f395c8e2fc31367ab603b35d42194","tid":232440,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>AMD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明顯有heart<br />\nIntel當班顧客狗咁撚</blockquote><br />\n數唔係咁計，呢單野明顯係amd未整好就丟出街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n Intel呢咁？<br />\nIntel條條ram上到？<br />\nIntel幾時會再更新？<br />\nIntel咪出啲矽脂撚人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nintel上唔到咩？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nIntel X99初期.對ram相容性非常差.同ryzen差唔多級數<br />\n<br />\n而且隔左好耐好耐.d廠商先慢慢再放新bios去改善<br />\n<br />\n講緊係真係隔左超過1年.到去到後期.出左6800K.X99都升級左粒chipset既時候先好好多<br />\n<br />\nAMD已經算做野快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都係個句.我唔理Intel定AMD.都唔應該係咁"},{"pid":"d669ad19eb32ce129d47724a97195986c71b35ea","tid":232440,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我完全唔介意呢單野，Ryzen 一出就已經買左用緊<br />\n但冇理由將呢d&quot;問題&quot;當成amd 有heart黎計架嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n試試intel整單一樣既野會唔會畀人屌到飛起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我只可以講.Ryzen的確係有誠意<br />\n<br />\n而AMD都跟進得算快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80faa6634e8